sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant Lambda as Guardrails Lambda
    participant DDB as DynamoDB (SensitiveRecords)
    participant GR as Bedrock Guardrails
    participant CW as CloudWatch Logs
    
    User->>Frontend: Query banking record
    Frontend->>APIGW: GET /guardrails/query
    APIGW->>Lambda: Invoke with payload
    
    Lambda->>DDB: GetItem
    
    Note over DDB: Raw data with SSN, Account, DOB
    
    DDB-->>Lambda: Return raw record (45ms)
    
    Lambda->>GR: ApplyGuardrail
    
    Note over GR: Detect and redact PII
    
    GR-->>Lambda: Sanitized record (120ms)
    
    Lambda->>CW: Log query metrics
    
    Lambda-->>APIGW: Return sanitized data
    APIGW-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: Display before/after
    
    Note over User,CW: Total latency: ~165ms
